This is one of the three games thereby presented with all their source code. 
This is a folder for the game Hangman.
Hangman is a game where from a database of words the player needs to guess a given word. In this exact game, the settings and the resources from the databse are set from the topic of Geography.

#Rules:
1. The player needs to guess one letter at a time which the word contains.
2. If the letter is correct it will be added to the word.
3. If the letter is false, a certain action will folow meaning the player will be closer to lose the game and be 'hanged'.
4. In order to win the game, you need to correctly guess all the letters for the given word.
5. We wish luck to all players and hope you are going to enjoy this game.

